title: Visible Supply of Corn for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Four Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1873-1889 (2)--Original Data, 1884-1889 (3)--Original, 1888-1927 (4)--Original, 1926-1940. Canada Is Included In The Data. Beginning In July 1885, In Transit Rail Is Excluded And It Is Also Unavailable Separately. Source: Chicago Board Of Trade, Annual Report.
